<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>How we rank betting sites</h2>
    <p>Our scoring framework uses seven weighted categories. No operator can buy a higher position: rankings reflect actual performance measured through our review process.</p>
    <div class="scoring-grid">
      <div class="scoring-item"><strong>Licensing and safety (25%)</strong><p>Provincial licence, clear ownership, visible terms, and accessible complaint route.</p></div>
      <div class="scoring-item"><strong>Banking and payouts (20%)</strong><p>Local payment coverage, withdrawal speed, KYC clarity, and payout reliability.</p></div>
      <div class="scoring-item"><strong>Bonus quality (15%)</strong><p>Real value after turnover, odds restrictions, deposit threshold and withdrawal caps.</p></div>
      <div class="scoring-item"><strong>Sport variety (15%)</strong><p>Market depth, live betting, bet builders and local sport coverage.</p></div>
      <div class="scoring-item"><strong>App and mobile (10%)</strong><p>Native app quality, browser performance, login speed and bet slip reliability.</p></div>
      <div class="scoring-item"><strong>Live betting (10%)</strong><p>In-play market depth, streaming availability and live cash-out function.</p></div>
      <div class="scoring-item"><strong>Customer support (5%)</strong><p>Response time, channel availability, WhatsApp and branch access.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>The law in one minute</h2>
    <div class="law-box">
      <p><strong>Licensed online sports betting is legal in South Africa.</strong> Every bookmaker on this site holds a provincial gambling licence.</p>
      <p><strong>Online casino and interactive gambling is not lawful</strong> under the current South African framework. This site does not promote or link to offshore online-casino operators.</p>
      <p>For casino-style entertainment, see our <a href="casinos-in-south-africa.html">land-based casino resort directory</a>. For draw-based play, see our <a href="national-lottery-south-africa.html">National Lottery guide</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-alt">
